      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some noticeable paint chips, minor door dings, and surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays some wear on the upholstery and plastic trim. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over showroom looks.",
